# When you use BAM Engine in your research, please cite both:
#   1. This software (citation below)
#   2. Macroeconomics from the Bottom-up (Delli Gatti et al., 2011) (citation in references)

cff-version: 1.2.0
message: 'If you use this software, please cite it along with the original BAM model (Delli Gatti et al., 2011).'
title: "BAM Engine: A Modular Python Framework for the BAM Agent-Based Macroeconomic Model"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Ganitis
    given-names: Konstantinos
    email: ganitiskostas@gmail.com
    affiliation: University of Piraeus, Greece
version: 0.7.0
date-released: 2026-03-13
